{"tid":933261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 華為危機】揭孟晚舟有第8本護照 持公務護照在港註冊董事 　","createTime":"2018-12-08T11:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:18:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a4cb28db35f0d88e9966daa02c50f785a1d858","tid":933261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"(內容更新)華為副董事長兼CFO孟晚舟仍未獲准保釋，案件延至溫哥華時間周一上午10時續審。美國司法部國際事務辦公室的一份文件指出孟晚舟近11年曾持有過4本中國護照及3本香港護照出入美國，稱她「完全有可能擁有美國政府不知道的額外護照」。另經《蘋果日報》記者查冊，發現她曾經於2004年在香港使用過一本中國「因公普通護照」註冊董事身份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181208/59006039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59006039&d=nT0JRHd2LMoASC6Ir7WJpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5c62a9bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59006039&h=a356c69b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181208/59006039</a>"},{"pid":"589fff001ce0b33dc9d2a8d527cb2f1fb5cce51a","tid":933261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"又多一本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c7379ad7136c68d505aabdb2027bb624fab16d","tid":933261,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ab4a50fa516eb599863524db1d688cfcf085d","tid":933261,"uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蘋果馬上將資料send俾美國司法部<br />\n佢肯定保釋唔到啦"},{"pid":"2ba4d6835a126416e9bf4a761d79e4c